credentials. If the header value is not present in the charset conversion table, a fallback mechanism is used to truncate it to a two characters value to allow a quick retry (for example, 'en-US' is truncated to 'en'). A header value of less than two characters forces an out of bound write of one NUL byte to a memory location that is not part of the string. In the worst case, quite unlikely, the process would crash which could be used as a Denial of Service attack. With 5.x after 5.6.28 or 7.x after 7.0.13, the issue is resolved in a non-default configuration with the opcache.validate_permission=1 setting. The vulnerability details are as follows. In PHP SAPIs where PHP interpreters share a common parent process, Zend OpCache creates a shared memory object owned by the common parent during initialization. Child PHP processes inherit the SHM descriptor, using it to cache and retrieve compiled script bytecode ("opcode" in PHP jargon). Cache keys vary depending on configuration, but filename is a central key component, and compiled opcode can generally be run if a script\'s filename is known or can be guessed. Many common shared-hosting configurations change EUID in child processes to enforce privilege separation among hosted users (for example using mod_ruid2 for the Apache HTTP Server, or php-fpm user settings). In these scenarios, the default Zend OpCache behavior defeats script file permissions by sharing a single SHM cache among all child PHP processes. PHP scripts often contain sensitive information: Think of CMS configurations where reading or running another user\'s script usually means gaining privileges to the CMS database.'}, 'CVE-2012-1823': If the header value is not present in the charset conversion table, a fallback mechanism is used to truncate it to a two characters value to allow a quick retry (for example, 'en-US' is truncated to 'en'). A header value of less than two characters forces an out of bound write of one NUL byte to a memory location that is not part of the string. In the worst case, quite unlikely, the process would crash which could be used as a Denial of Service attack. class="page_header floating_element">\n        <img src="/icons/ubuntu-logo.png" alt="Ubuntu Logo" class="floating_element"/>\n        <span class="floating_element">\n          Apache2 Ubuntu Default Page\n        </span>\n      </div>\n<!--      <div class="table_of_contents floating_element">\n        <div class="section_header section_header_grey">\n          TABLE OF CONTENTS\n        </div>\n        <div class="table_of_contents_item floating_element">\n          <a href="#about">About</a>\n        </div>\n        <div class="table_of_contents_item floating_element">\n          <a href="#changes">Changes</a>\n        </div>\n        <div class="table_of_contents_item floating_element">\n          <a href="#scope">Scope</a>\n        </div>\n        <div class="table_of_contents_item floating_element">\n          <a href="#files">Config files</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n-->\n      <div class="content_section floating_element">\n\n\n        <div class="section_header section_header_red">\n          <div id="about"></div>\n          It works!\n        </div>\n        <div class="content_section_text">\n          <p>\n                This is the default welcome page used to test the correct \n                operation of the Apache2 server after installation on Ubuntu systems.\n                It is based on the equivalent page on Debian, from which the Ubuntu Apache\n                packaging is derived.\n                If you can read this page, it means that the Apache HTTP server installed at\n                this site is working properly. You should <b>replace this file</b> (located at\n                <tt>/var/www/html/index.html</tt>) before continuing to operate your HTTP server.\n          </p>\n\n\n          <p>\n                If you are a normal user of this web site and don\'t know what this page is\n                about, this probably means that the site is currently unavailable due to\n                maintenance.\n                If the problem persists, please contact the site\'s administrator.\n          </p>\n\n        </div>\n        <div class="section_header">\n          <div id="changes"></div>\n                Configuration Overview\n        </div>\n        <div class="content_section_text">\n          <p>\n                Ubuntu\'s Apache2 default configuration is different from the\n                upstream default configuration, and split into several files optimized for\n                interaction with Ubuntu tools. The configuration system is\n                <b>fully documented in\n                /usr/share/doc/apache2/README.Debian.gz</b>. Refer to this for the full\n                documentation. Documentation for the web server itself can be\n                found by accessing the <a href="/manual">manual</a> if the <tt>apache2-doc</tt>\n                package was installed on this server.\n\n          </p>\n          <p>\n                The configuration layout for an Apache2 web server installation on Ubuntu systems is as follows:\n          </p>\n          <pre>\n/etc/apache2/\n|-- apache2.conf\n|       `--  ports.conf\n|-- mods-enabled\n|       |-- *.load\n|       `-- *.conf\n|-- conf-enabled\n|       `-- *.conf\n|-- sites-enabled\n|       `-- *.conf\n          </pre>\n          <ul>\n                        <li>\n                           <tt>apache2.conf</tt> is the main configuration\n                           file. It puts the pieces together by including all remaining configuration\n                           files when starting up the web server.\n                        </li>\n\n                        <li>\n                           <tt>ports.conf</tt> is always included from the\n                           main configuration file. It is used to determine the listening ports for\n                           incoming connections, and this file can be customized anytime.\n                        </li>\n\n                        <li>\n                           Configuration files in the <tt>mods-enabled/</tt>,\n                           <tt>conf-enabled/</tt> and <tt>sites-enabled/</tt> directories contain\n                           particular configuration snippets which manage modules, global configuration\n                           fragments, or virtual host configurations, respectively.\n                        </li>\n\n                        <li>\n                           They are activated by symlinking available\n                           configuration files from their respective\n                           *-available/ counterparts. These should be managed\n                           by using our helpers\n                           <tt>\n                                <a href="http://manpages.debian.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=a2enmod">a2enmod</a>,\n                                <a href="http://manpages.debian.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=a2dismod">a2dismod</a>,\n                           </tt>\n                           <tt>\n                                <a href="http://manpages.debian.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=a2ensite">a2ensite</a>,\n                                <a href="http://manpages.debian.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=a2dissite">a2dissite</a>,\n                            </tt>\n                                and\n                           <tt>\n                                <a href="http://manpages.debian.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=a2enconf">a2enconf</a>,\n                                <a href="http://manpages.debian.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=a2disconf">a2disconf</a>\n                           </tt>. See their respective man pages for detailed information.\n                        </li>\n\n                        <li>\n                           The binary is called apache2. Due to the use of\n                           environment variables, in the default configuration, apache2 needs to be\n                           started/stopped with <tt>/etc/init.d/apache2</tt> or <tt>apache2ctl</tt>.\n                           <b>Calling <tt>/usr/bin/apache2</tt> directly will not work</b> with the\n                           default configuration.\n                        </li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class="section_header">\n            <div id="docroot"></div>\n                Document Roots\n        </div>\n\n        <div class="content_section_text">\n            <p>\n                By default, Ubuntu does not allow access through the web browser to\n                <em>any</em> file apart of those located in <tt>/var/www</tt>,\n                <a href="http://httpd.apache.org/docs/2.4/mod/mod_userdir.html">public_html</a>\n                directories (when enabled) and <tt>/usr/share</tt> (for web\n                applications). If your site is using a web document root\n                located elsewhere (such as in <tt>/srv</tt>) you may need to whitelist your\n                document root directory in <tt>/etc/apache2/apache2.conf</tt>.\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                The default Ubuntu document root is <tt>/var/www/html</tt>. You\n                can make your own virtual hosts under /var/www. href="http://198.11.180.45/2018/08/ios-app-store-review-guidelines/" rel="bookmark">iOS App Store Review Guidelines 探讨</a></h2>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class="entry-meta">\n\t\t\t<span class="posted-on"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2018/08/ios-app-store-review-guidelines/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2018-08-22T10:07:14+08:00">2018-08-22</time></a></span><span class="byline"> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://198.11.180.45/author/yul/">Rick Luo</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2018/08/ios-app-store-review-guidelines/#respond">Leave a comment</a></span>\t\t</div><!-- .entry-meta -->\n\t\t\t</header><!-- .entry-header -->\n\n\t<div class="entry-content">\n\t\t<h3>前</h3>\n<p>首先, 这里是<a href="https://developer.apple.com/app-store/review/guidelines/">App Store Review Guidelines</a>的官网链接.<br />\n啥都要以它为准, <del datetime="2018-08-16T09:09:08+00:00">(哪怕是觉得他们错了要申诉)</del>.</p>\n<h3>“大礼包”</h3>\n<p>最近才从前公司组里同事那听来这个词, 有点有趣.<br />\n在网上看了看大家提的审核问题, 很快就发现了诸如“2.1大礼包”, “4.3大礼包”, “礼包5.0”等等有趣的叫法.<br />\n想必是些个坎吧.</p>\n<h3>2.1 App Completeness</h3>\n<p>程序完备性.<br />\n个人感觉这一块的问题应该算是可以比较容易解决的问题.<br />\n某种程度上, 是提交方自己没做好的.<br />\n按照指示修复问题即可.</p>\n<h3>2.3 Accurate Metadata</h3>\n<p>很常见的, 应用程序元数据不准确.<br />\n这里可见Apple的要求比较严格. (我碰到的审核问题大部分都在这一块).</p>\n<p>列举常见的此类问题:<br />\n&#8211; screenshot: 目前对于手机应用, 必传的图有iPhone X/iPhone 8 Plus的尺寸图; 需要注意的是, 图中若出现iPhone, 则需反应对应图片所指代的iPhone(也就是说iPhoneX的图里的手机必须是iPhone X, iPhone Plus里则是普通iPhone).<br />\n&#8211; 应用介绍内容和应用程序不一致; 不要写太宽泛就好; 需要注意的是, 一些诸如医疗、慈善等相关的内容, 需要发布公司/单位即该内容的提供方, 要不然是肯定不会通过的.<br />\n&#8211; 搜索关键字;</p>\n<h3>4.3 Spam</h3>\n<p>导引上说“Don’t create multiple Bundle IDs of the same app.”<br />\n看来这条是重复包改名提交的行为了.<br />\n这个我可没做过.<br />\n不过试想了一下, 如果真有这种需求, 改动一点再提交吧, 对于有开发人员的情况, 这应该不是什么大问题.<br />\n<del>如果只是买了别人的应用代码就想提交的话..恐怕会遇到此问题.</del></p>\n<p>相关审核规则:<br />\n4.3.0 &#8211; Are a duplicate of another app or are conspicuously similar to another app</p>\n<h3>IAP应用内购相关</h3>\n<p>积分or类似积分形式, 数字消耗品, App内消耗品等类似形式的购买物, 都应走In-App Purchase(应用内购).</p>\n<p>列举相关:<br />\n3.1.1 &#8211; Use payment mechanisms other than in-app purchase to unlock features or functionality in the app</p>\n<h3>隐藏功能相关</h3>\n<p>若Apple审核以某种手段检测or怀疑提交审核的应用包含隐藏功能, 可能列举如下条款:</p>\n<p>1.1.6 &#8211; Include false information, features, or misleading metadata.<br />\n2.3.0 &#8211; Undergo significant concept changes after approval<br />\n2.3.1 &#8211; Have hidden or undocumented features, including hidden &#8220;switches&#8221; that redirect to a gambling or lottery website</p>\n<p>这里说得很明确了, 隐藏功能, 审核通过后会出现重大功能变更&#8230;<br />\n马甲包的问题在此.</p>\n<h3>Legal 法律相关问题</h3>\n<p>基本指明了, 若要提供相关服务, 必须是具有该资质的机构/公司/单位提交应用.</p>\n<p>5.2.1 &#8211; Were not submitted by the legal entity that owns and is responsible for offering any services provided by the app<br />\n5.2.3 &#8211; Facilitate illegal file sharing or include the ability to save, convert, or download media from third party sources without explicit authorization from those sources<br />\n5.3.4 &#8211; Do not have the necessary licensing and permissions for all the locations where the app is used</p>\n<p>借贷问题相关:<br />\n3.2.1 &#8211; Do not come from the financial institution performing the loan services<br />\n具有资质的机构才能提交借贷相关功能的应用.</p>\n<h3>Author</h3>\n<p>骆昱(<a href="http://luoyu.space">Luo Yu</a>)</p>\n<p>Email: <a href="mailto:indie.luo@gmail.com">indie.luo@gmail.com</a></p>\n<h4>Version</h4>\n<p>1.0.0, Thursday, August 16, 2018</p>\n<p></p>\n\n\t\t\t</div><!-- .entry-content -->\n\n    <footer class="entry-footer">\n        <span class="cat-links">Posted in <a href="http://198.11.180.45/category/stuff/" rel="category tag">stuff</a></span><span class="tags-links">Tagged <a href="http://198.11.180.45/tag/appstore/" rel="tag">appstore</a>, <a href="http://198.11.180.45/tag/ios/" rel="tag">iOS</a>, <a href="http://198.11.180.45/tag/review/" rel="tag">review</a></span>    </footer><!-- .entry-footer -->\n</article><!-- #post-## -->\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n<article id="post-811" class="post-811 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-stuff tag-56 tag-design tag-ios tag-ui tag-wwdc">\n \t<header class="entry-header">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2018/08/note-wwdc-2016-session-805-iterative-ui-design/" rel="bookmark">笔记: WWDC 2016 Session 805 Iterative UI Design</a></h2>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class="entry-meta">\n\t\t\t<span class="posted-on"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2018/08/note-wwdc-2016-session-805-iterative-ui-design/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2018-08-14T11:20:55+08:00">2018-08-14</time><time class="updated" datetime="2018-08-21T11:16:23+08:00">2018-08-21</time></a></span><span class="byline"> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://198.11.180.45/author/yul/">Rick Luo</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2018/08/note-wwdc-2016-session-805-iterative-ui-design/#respond">Leave a comment</a></span>\t\t</div><!-- .entry-meta -->\n\t\t\t</header><!-- .entry-header -->\n\n\t<div class="entry-content">\n\t\t<h3>前面</h3>\n<p>最近在翻看WWDC视频.<br />\n这个属于原型设计块的内容, 以前也确实没有发掘看看.<br />\n觉得还不错, 有很多更Apple风格的思路. 留点笔记吧.</p>\n<h3>笔记</h3>\n<p>805所说的迭代UI设计, 更多的是在讲如何从零开始设计一个App.<br />\n迭代的, 是产品设计的实现过程.</p>\n<p>围绕一些问题, 可以来梳理思路:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>What are we making?</li>\n<li>Who is it for?</li>\n<li>Does it actually work?</li>\n<li>And did we get it right?</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote><p>\n  Identify the features that matter most to the people who will use your app,<br />\n  and features that serve your own goals for the app it self.<br />\n  In order to determine what your app should do.\n</p></blockquote>\n<p>还大字说明了一件感觉很多“产品经理”应该好好看看的&#8211;</p>\n<pre><code>You ≠ User\n</code></pre>\n<p>你不是用户.</p>\n<blockquote><p>\n  Designing for yourself distracts you from what matters most to everyone else.\n</p></blockquote>\n<p>诸多产品经理喜欢用自己的习惯, 套上“用户”如何如何想, “用户”如何如何觉得这样的外衣, 来解读需求.<br />\n应该注意注意啦.</p>\n<p>视频里还演示了用Keynote来画UI的过程, 并归纳了一下:<br />\n1. Use screenshots as references;<br />\n2. Draw some squares and lines;<br />\n3. Zoom in and out a lot (to make sure that they were pixel perfect);<br />\n4. Use believable content.</p>\n<p>设计完一个界面后, 再继续延展.<br />\n因为一屏界面不是一个App, 需要完善workflow.</p>\n<p>基本原则还是:</p>\n<blockquote><p>\n  Started with what I knew and then I evaluated and iterated on all my designs until I ended up with something I was happy with.\n</p></blockquote>\n<p>整个过程就是805所在提的, iterative design, 迭代设计.</p>\n<h3>尾</h3>\n<p>实际看来, 他们的操作, 有多设计, 多比较, 比我日常看到的有更多的互动.<br />\n而不是一个人盯着一屏幕的工具, 和别人家的产品, 埋头~~抄抄抄~~画画画.</p>\n<h3>Author</h3>\n<p>骆昱(<a href="http://open.luoyu.space">Luo Yu</a>, <a href="mailto:indie.luo@gmail.com">indie.luo@gmail.com</a>)<br />\nTuesday, August 14, 2018</p>\n\n\t\t\t</div><!-- .entry-content -->\n\n    <footer class="entry-footer">\n        <span class="cat-links">Posted in <a href="http://198.11.180.45/category/stuff/" rel="category tag">stuff</a></span><span class="tags-links">Tagged <a href="http://198.11.180.45/tag/2016/" rel="tag">2016</a>, <a href="http://198.11.180.45/tag/design/" rel="tag">design</a>, <a href="http://198.11.180.45/tag/ios/" rel="tag">iOS</a>, <a href="http://198.11.180.45/tag/ui/" rel="tag">UI</a>, <a href="http://198.11.180.45/tag/wwdc/" rel="tag">wwdc</a></span>    </footer><!-- .entry-footer -->\n</article><!-- #post-## -->\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n<article id="post-788" class="post-788 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-stuff tag-archlinunx tag-installation">\n \t<header class="entry-header">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2018/04/note-archlinux-installation/" rel="bookmark">笔记: ArchLinux环境</a></h2>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class="entry-meta">\n\t\t\t<span class="posted-on"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2018/04/note-archlinux-installation/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2018-04-21T18:45:19+08:00">2018-04-21</time><time class="updated" datetime="2018-08-21T11:16:50+08:00">2018-08-21</time></a></span><span class="byline"> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://198.11.180.45/author/yul/">Rick Luo</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2018/04/note-archlinux-installation/#respond">Leave a comment</a></span>\t\t</div><!-- .entry-meta -->\n\t\t\t</header><!-- .entry-header -->\n\n\t<div class="entry-content">\n\t\t<p>最近把旧电脑的坏硬盘换下来, 然后立马元气满满的样子. 就准备给它装个Linux来用.</p>\n<p>另外好久没有更新，就把东西放上来好了.</p>\n<h3>准备安装U盘</h3>\n<p>从ArchLinux的官网下载最新的iso文件，文件很小.</p>\n<p>然后用它制作启动U盘，因为在Mac中，就直接可以<code>dd</code>到U盘的设备.</p>\n<h3>启动安装环境</h3>\n<p>连接U盘，从U盘启动，进入安装环境.</p>\n<p>先连上Wifi:</p>\n<pre><code class="language-bash">wifi-menu\n</code></pre>\n<p>从选择到配置都很简单.</p>\n<p>也可随便<code>ping</code>个地址看连好了没.</p>\n<p>准备硬盘空间了:</p>\n<pre><code class="language-bash">fdisk -l\n</code></pre>\n<p>列举了磁盘的情况.</p>\n<p>我就用<code>cfdisk</code>分区了.</p>\n<p>初次进，会让选择分区表类型，配合电脑这边就用的<code>MBR</code>.</p>\n<p>创建一个<code>primary</code>分区，准备挂载<code>/</code>，标记上<code>bootable</code>;</p>\n<p>因为主硬盘只有120G的SSD，准备在副硬盘上挂数据，这里就不多分区了;</p>\n<p>然后准备一个<code>swap</code>分区.</p>\n<p>然后<code>write</code>改变，退出 <em>cfdisk</em>.</p>\n<p>接下来格式化硬盘，</p>\n<pre><code class="language-bash">mkfs.ext4 /dev/sda1\nmkswap /dev/sda2\n</code></pre>\n<p>好了就可以激活swap,</p>\n<pre><code class="language-bash">swapon /dev/sda2\n</code></pre>\n<p>挂载分区:</p>\n<pre><code class="language-bash">mount /dev/sda1 /mnt\n</code></pre>\n<h3>安装系统</h3>\n<pre><code class="language-bash">pacstrap /mnt base\n# 也可加上 base-devel\n</code></pre>\n<p>等它下载安装完以后，</p>\n<p>创建fstab文件:</p>\n<pre><code class="language-bash">genfstab /mnt &gt;&gt; /mnt/etc/fstab\n</code></pre>\n<p>这就可以change-root了:</p>\n<pre><code class="language-bash">arch-chroot /mnt #/bin/bash\n</code></pre>\n<h3>修改系统的配置</h3>\n<p>取消<code>/etc/locale.gen</code>文件里<code>en_US.UTF-8</code>的注释,</p>\n<p>这个以后配置中文也要对应放开里面相关的项目,</p>\n<p>然后激活它:</p>\n<pre><code class="language-bash">locale-gen\n</code></pre>\n<p>输出一个<code>/etc/locale.conf</code>文件:</p>\n<pre><code class="language-bash">echo \'LANG=en_US.UTF-8\' &gt; /etc/locale.conf\n</code></pre>\n<p>链接一下配置时区:</p>\n<pre><code class="language-bash">ln -sf /usr/share/zoneinfo/Asia/Shanghai /etc/localtime\n</code></pre>\n<p>同步时间:</p>\n<pre><code class="language-bash">hwclock --systohc # --utc\n</code></pre>\n<p>可以<code>date</code>试试看输出时间对不～</p>\n<p>设置<strong>root</strong>密码:</p>\n<pre><code class="language-bash">passwd\n</code></pre>\n<p>设置hostname:</p>\n<pre><code class="language-bash">echo mr_luo_arch &gt; /etc/hostname\n</code></pre>\n<p>启用<code>dhcpcd</code>:</p>\n<pre><code class="language-bash">systemctl enable dhcpcd\n</code></pre>\n<h3>安装bootloader</h3>\n<p>先安装好<code>grub</code>:</p>\n<pre><code class="language-bash">pacman -S grub os-prober\n</code></pre>\n<p>安装grub引导,</p>\n<pre><code class="language-bash">grub-install /dev/sda\n</code></pre>\n<p>生成配置:</p>\n<pre><code class="language-bash">grub-mkconfig -o /boot/grub/grub.cfg\n</code></pre>\n<p>这里基础系统就装好了.</p>\n<h3>其他安装</h3>\n<p>不过我顺便装上桌面环境，最近觉得gnome3用着挺顺手的,</p>\n<pre><code class="language-bash"># 安装相关的包\npacman -Sy --nocomfirm gnome gnome-extra\n\n# 启用gdm\nsystemctl enable gdm\n</code></pre>\n<p>这里的Gnome还少一个网络配置管理的工具，</p>\n<p>顺道给它装上:</p>\n<pre><code class="language-bash"># 安装相关的包\npacman -S networkmanager\n\n# 启用\nsystemctl enable NetworkManager\n</code></pre>\n<p>给加一个普通用户:</p>\n<pre><code class="language-bash">useradd -m -s /bin/bash NewUserName\n# -m 创建home目录\n# -s 设置默认shell\n\n# 给它配置密码\npasswd NewUserName\n</code></pre>\n<p>编辑<code>/etc/sudoers</code>文件，加上:</p>\n<pre><code class="language-bash">NewUserName ALL=(ALL) ALL\n</code></pre>\n<p>这样新用户可以用上sudo.</p>\n<h3>结束</h3>\n<p>退出change-root，重启就好啦～</p>\n<pre><code class="language-bash">exit\nreboot\n</code></pre>\n<h3>Author</h3>\n<p><a href="http://luoyu.space">骆昱</a></p>\n\n\t\t\t</div><!-- .entry-content -->\n\n    <footer class="entry-footer">\n        <span class="cat-links">Posted in <a href="http://198.11.180.45/category/stuff/" rel="category tag">stuff</a></span><span class="tags-links">Tagged <a href="http://198.11.180.45/tag/archlinunx/" rel="tag">archlinunx</a>, <a href="http://198.11.180.45/tag/installation/" rel="tag">installation</a></span>    </footer><!-- .entry-footer -->\n</article><!-- #post-## -->\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n<article id="post-744" class="post-744 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-dev tag-docker tag-production">\n \t<header class="entry-header">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2017/09/docker-in-production/" rel="bookmark">Docker in Production 笔记</a></h2>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class="entry-meta">\n\t\t\t<span class="posted-on"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2017/09/docker-in-production/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2017-09-25T13:58:12+08:00">2017-09-25</time><time class="updated" datetime="2017-09-28T15:43:32+08:00">2017-09-28</time></a></span><span class="byline"> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://198.11.180.45/author/yul/">Rick Luo</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2017/09/docker-in-production/#comments">2 Comments</a></span>\t\t</div><!-- .entry-meta -->\n\t\t\t</header><!-- .entry-header -->\n\n\t<div class="entry-content">\n\t\t<h3>In production</h3>\n<p><img src="https://i1.wp.com/wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/681fb919gy1fjtoc5s8g7j21400qon5r.jpg?w=739" alt="docker-workshop-thought-works" data-recalc-dims="1" /></p>\n<p>上周六参加了thoughtworks的docker workshop活动, 主要探讨了docker技术在生产环境应用的问题.</p>\n<p>前面介绍了一下容器相关技术, 如<code>Linux Container(lxc)</code>, 也介绍了namespace隔离等等.</p>\n<p>还有docker的架构:</p>\n<p><img src="https://docs.docker.com/engine/article-img/architecture.svg" alt="docker-architecture" /></p>\n<p>然后又有部分常见的docker使用技术, 如<code>docker compose</code>, 使用compose.yml文件指定容器的创建, 以及整体管理等.</p>\n<h3>进阶</h3>\n<p>文件系统的挂载, 包括数据卷挂载(-v), 以及制作+使用数据容器的思路方向.</p>\n<p>容器网络模型, host内的bridge, 跨host的overlay, 以及sandbox/endpoint定义.</p>\n<p><img src="https://i1.wp.com/wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/681fb919gy1fjvsiji9coj20nk0gxdkm.jpg?w=739" alt="docker-network" data-recalc-dims="1" /></p>\n<p>也扩展了一下安全性问题. (docker真的权限&#8230;太高了)</p>\n<h3>多主机部署于服务发现</h3>\n<p>Consul服务发现.</p>\n<p>Registrator服务注册.</p>\n<p>Docker Swarm集群.</p>\n<h3>日志/监控</h3>\n<p>docker logs的使用局限.</p>\n<h3>一点关于实际应用的思考</h3>\n<p>在docker的助力下，将每个服务，做成一个容器，然后跑在公司所有的主机上，这样的微服务架构想想就知道才是当下最合理的方式。</p>\n<p>借助cluster解决方案，可以将公司的多服务器主机的资源合起来利用，并能更好的应对服务故障。</p>\n<p>而容器微服务，在开发本地调试，一旦通过测试可以发布，发布的过程也是简单而不会出错。</p>\n<p>构建好如上讲述的服务注册+发现，更能动态获取服务地址，自动完成服务之间的连接，才称得上是科学做法。</p>\n<p>而服务状态监控，健康检查，日志收集处理，这些服务构建好，才能真的在出错时及时追溯问题，更能通过预警邮件及时知道问题。</p>\n<p>一个产品环境，必须是科学专业的环境，而不是单单能运行就行。</p>\n\n\t\t\t</div><!-- .entry-content -->\n\n    <footer class="entry-footer">\n        <span class="cat-links">Posted in <a href="http://198.11.180.45/category/dev/" rel="category tag">dev</a></span><span class="tags-links">Tagged <a href="http://198.11.180.45/tag/docker/" rel="tag">docker</a>, <a href="http://198.11.180.45/tag/production/" rel="tag">production</a></span>    </footer><!-- .entry-footer -->\n</article><!-- #post-## -->\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n<article id="post-732" class="post-732 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-stuff tag-rust">\n \t<header class="entry-header">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2017/09/rust-lang-notes-day-2/" rel="bookmark">Rust-Lang Notes | Day 2</a></h2>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class="entry-meta">\n\t\t\t<span class="posted-on"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2017/09/rust-lang-notes-day-2/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2017-09-13T13:42:41+08:00">2017-09-13</time><time class="updated" datetime="2017-10-09T13:52:50+08:00">2017-10-09</time></a></span><span class="byline"> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://198.11.180.45/author/yul/">Rick Luo</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2017/09/rust-lang-notes-day-2/#respond">Leave a comment</a></span>\t\t</div><!-- .entry-meta -->\n\t\t\t</header><!-- .entry-header -->\n\n\t<div class="entry-content">\n\t\t<h3>General</h3>\n<h4>变量</h4>\n<p>变量默认是<strong>不可变immutable</strong>的.</p>\n<pre><code class="rust">let x = 5;\nx = 6; // ERROR: re-assignment of immutable variable\n</code></pre>\n<p>mut关键字声明可变的变量.</p>\n<pre><code class="rust">let mut x = 5;\nx = 6;\n</code></pre>\n<h4>常量 constants</h4>\n<p>声明常量使用<code>const</code>关键字, 且不允许使用<code>mut</code>.</p>\n<p><strong>常量不光默认不能变，它总是不能变.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>而且<strong>必须</strong>注明值的类型.</strong></p>\n<pre><code class="rust">const MAX_POINTS: u32 = 100_000;\n// 声明一个常量MAX_POINTS, 值是100,000.\n</code></pre>\n<p>常量在整个程序生命周期中都有效，位于它声明的作用域之中.</p>\n<p>这使得常量可以作为多处代码使用的全局范围的值.</p>\n<p>将用于整个程序的硬编码的值声明为常量对后来的维护者了解值的意义很用帮助。它也能将硬编码的值汇总一处，为将来可能的修改提供方便。</p>\n<h4>隐藏（Shadowing）</h4>\n<p>重复使用<code>let</code>关键字来隐藏.</p>\n\n\t\t\t</div><!-- .entry-content -->\n\n    <footer class="entry-footer">\n        <span class="cat-links">Posted in <a href="http://198.11.180.45/category/stuff/" rel="category tag">stuff</a></span><span class="tags-links">Tagged <a href="http://198.11.180.45/tag/rust/" rel="tag">rust</a></span>    </footer><!-- .entry-footer -->\n</article><!-- #post-## -->\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n<article id="post-720" class="post-720 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-dev tag-rust">\n \t<header class="entry-header">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2017/09/rust-lang-notes/" rel="bookmark">Rust-Lang Notes</a></h2>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class="entry-meta">\n\t\t\t<span class="posted-on"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2017/09/rust-lang-notes/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2017-09-12T15:32:05+08:00">2017-09-12</time><time class="updated" datetime="2017-09-12T17:35:05+08:00">2017-09-12</time></a></span><span class="byline"> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://198.11.180.45/author/yul/">Rick Luo</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2017/09/rust-lang-notes/#respond">Leave a comment</a></span>\t\t</div><!-- .entry-meta -->\n\t\t\t</header><!-- .entry-header -->\n\n\t<div class="entry-content">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="post-thumbnail">\n\t\t\t\t<a href="http://198.11.180.45/2017/09/rust-lang-notes/"><img width="370" height="130" src="https://i2.wp.com/198.11.180.45/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/rust-lang-notes-spe.jpg?fit=370%2C130" class="attachment-libre-2-post-thumbnail size-libre-2-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" data-attachment-id="730" data-permalink="http://198.11.180.45/rust-lang-notes-spe/" data-orig-file="https://i2.wp.com/198.11.180.45/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/rust-lang-notes-spe.jpg?fit=370%2C130" data-orig-size="370,130" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="rust-lang-notes-spe" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://i2.wp.com/198.11.180.45/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/rust-lang-notes-spe.jpg?fit=300%2C105" data-large-file="https://i2.wp.com/198.11.180.45/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/rust-lang-notes-spe.jpg?fit=370%2C130" /></a>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<h3>Rust语言学习笔记</h3>\n<h3>Installation 安装</h3>\n<p>习惯的</p>\n<pre><code>$ brew search rust\n==&gt; Searching local taps...\nrust       rustc-completion       rustup-init      uncrustify\n</code></pre>\n<p>然后顺手就可以:</p>\n<pre><code>$ brew install rust\n</code></pre>\n<p>这样安装完之后是可以使用rustc等的.</p>\n<p>然而缺少rustup工具, 也因为brew同一管理路径的原因, 缺失<code>~/.cargo</code>目录, (不知道为啥没有至少一个软连接?).</p>\n<p>所以出于学习阶段(在我还没弄清谁更好时), 先使用官方的方法(况且cargo是Rust的package manager):</p>\n<p>如果brew安装过的, 别忘了先<code>brew uninstall rust</code>卸载掉.</p>\n<pre><code class="bash">$ curl https://sh.rustup.rs -sSf | sh\ninfo: downloading installer\n\nWelcome to Rust!\n\nThis will download and install the official compiler for the Rust programming\nlanguage, and its package manager, Cargo.\n\nIt will add the cargo, rustc, rustup and other commands to Cargo\'s bin\ndirectory, located at:\n\n  /Users/blodely/.cargo/bin\n\nThis path will then be added to your PATH environment variable by modifying the\nprofile files located at:\n\n  /Users/blodely/.profile\n  /Users/blodely/.zprofile\n\nYou can uninstall at any time with rustup self uninstall and these changes will\nbe reverted.\n\nCurrent installation options:\n\n   default host triple: x86_64-apple-darwin\n     default toolchain: stable\n  modify PATH variable: yes\n\n1) Proceed with installation (default)\n2) Customize installation\n3) Cancel installation\n1\n\ninfo: syncing channel updates for \'stable-x86_64-apple-darwin\'\ninfo: latest update on 2017-08-31, rust version 1.20.0 (f3d6973f4 2017-08-27)\ninfo: downloading component \'rustc\'\n 35.1 MiB /  35.1 MiB (100 %) 121.6 KiB/s ETA:   0 s\ninfo: downloading component \'rust-std\'\n 49.0 MiB /  49.0 MiB (100 %) 128.0 KiB/s ETA:   0 s\ninfo: downloading component \'cargo\'\n  2.6 MiB /   2.6 MiB (100 %) 124.8 KiB/s ETA:   0 s\ninfo: downloading component \'rust-docs\'\n  3.6 MiB /   3.6 MiB (100 %) 115.2 KiB/s ETA:   0 s\ninfo: installing component \'rustc\'\ninfo: installing component \'rust-std\'\ninfo: installing component \'cargo\'\ninfo: installing component \'rust-docs\'\ninfo: default toolchain set to \'stable\'\n\n  stable installed - rustc 1.20.0 (f3d6973f4 2017-08-27)\n\n\nRust is installed now. Great!\n\nTo get started you need Cargo\'s bin directory ($HOME/.cargo/bin) in your PATH\nenvironment variable. Next time you log in this will be done automatically.\n\nTo configure your current shell run source $HOME/.cargo/env\n</code></pre>\n<p>这里当然猴急的运行<code>source $HOME/.cargo/env</code>,</p>\n<p>再就测试一下:</p>\n<pre><code class="bash">$ rustc --version\nrustc 1.20.0 (f3d6973f4 2017-08-27)\n</code></pre>\n<p>一切正常.</p>\n<h3>Hello, world</h3>\n<pre><code class="bash">$ vim main.rs\n</code></pre>\n<p>然后录入:</p>\n<pre><code class="rust">fn main() {\n    println!("Hello, world!~");\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>编译:</p>\n<pre><code class="bash">$ rustc main.rs\n</code></pre>\n<p>运行二进制文件:</p>\n<pre><code class="bash">$ ./main\nHello, world!~\n</code></pre>\n<h3>Cargo</h3>\n<p>Cargo命令给出的解释是: Rust&#8217;s package manager.</p>\n<p>好吧, 使用Cargo来创建一个工程看看.</p>\n<pre><code class="bash">$ cargo new hello_cargo --bin\n    Created binary (application) `hello_cargo` project\n</code></pre>\n<p>这样就创建了一个binary即应用程序(而不是一个库)的工程了.</p>\n<p><code>cd</code>进去发现, 还给默认初始化成一个git仓库了.</p>\n<pre><code class="bash">$ git status\nOn branch master\n\nInitial commit\n\nUntracked files:\n  (use "git add &lt;file&gt;..." to include in what will be committed)\n\n    .gitignore\n    Cargo.toml\n    src/\n</code></pre>\n<p>文件结构已归好, 还增加<code>git ignore</code>文件.</p>\n<p>查阅文档, <code>--vcs</code>参数可控制此项.</p>\n<p>然后这个<code>Cargo.toml</code>文件类型让我为之一震&#8230;</p>\n<p>toml = Tom&#8217;s Obvious, Minimal Language <a href="https://github.com/toml-lang/toml">GithubRepo</a></p>\n<pre><code class="bash">$ cat Cargo.toml\n[package] # 段落标题; 配置一个包\nname = "hello_cargo"\nversion = "0.1.0"\nauthors = ["Luo Yu &lt;indie.luo@gmail.com&gt;"]\n\n[dependencies] # 项目依赖的crates列表(crate: Rust代码包)\n</code></pre>\n<p>构建与运行:</p>\n<pre><code class="bash">$ cargo build # cargo run\n   Compiling hello_cargo v0.1.0 (file:///Users/blodely/Desktop/hello_cargo)\n    Finished dev [unoptimized + debuginfo] target(s) in 3.27 secs\n$ ./target/debug/hello_cargo\nHello, world!\n</code></pre>\n<h3>Author</h3>\n<p>Luo Yu</p>\n<p>indie.luo@gmail.com</p>\n<p>Tuesday, September 12, 2017</p>\n\n\t\t\t</div><!-- .entry-content -->\n\n    <footer class="entry-footer">\n        <span class="cat-links">Posted in <a &#8211; CoreML, ML即Machine Learning.</p>\n<p>官方给出的架构如下图:</p>\n<p><img src="https://i2.wp.com/wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/681fb919gy1fjgrxso03oj20f0092t9c.jpg?w=739" alt="CoreML-framework-arc" data-recalc-dims="1" /></p>\n<p>如图可见, 该框的几个实现包括Vision, 还有NLP.</p>\n<h3>NLP (Natural Language Processing)</h3>\n<p>常有功能:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Language Identification</li>\n<li>Named Entity Recognition</li>\n</ul>\n<p>架构:</p>\n<p><img src="https://i2.wp.com/wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/681fb919ly1fjgserix9zj20g408g75d.jpg?w=739" alt="NLP-arch" data-recalc-dims="1" /></p>\n<p>这么一来, 封装后使用变得简单.</p>\n<h3>NSLinguisticTagger</h3>\n\n\t\t\t</div><!-- .entry-content -->\n\n    <footer class="entry-footer">\n        <span class="cat-links">Posted in <a has-post-thumbnail hentry category-dev tag-basic tag-emacs">\n \t<header class="entry-header">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2017/09/emacs-notes/" rel="bookmark">Emacs 新手笔记</a></h2>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class="entry-meta">\n\t\t\t<span class="posted-on"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2017/09/emacs-notes/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2017-09-08T16:51:01+08:00">2017-09-08</time><time class="updated" datetime="2017-09-08T17:45:45+08:00">2017-09-08</time></a></span><span class="byline"> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://198.11.180.45/author/yul/">Rick Luo</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2017/09/emacs-notes/#respond">Leave a comment</a></span>\t\t</div><!-- .entry-meta -->\n\t\t\t</header><!-- .entry-header -->\n\n\t<div class="entry-content">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="post-thumbnail">\n\t\t\t\t<a href="http://198.11.180.45/2017/09/emacs-notes/"><img width="370" height="130" src="https://i0.wp.com/198.11.180.45/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/emacs-notes-spe.jpg?fit=370%2C130" class="attachment-libre-2-post-thumbnail size-libre-2-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" data-attachment-id="710" data-permalink="http://198.11.180.45/emacs-notes-spe/" data-orig-file="https://i0.wp.com/198.11.180.45/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/emacs-notes-spe.jpg?fit=370%2C130" data-orig-size="370,130" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="emacs-notes-spe" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://i0.wp.com/198.11.180.45/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/emacs-notes-spe.jpg?fit=300%2C105" data-large-file="https://i0.wp.com/198.11.180.45/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/emacs-notes-spe.jpg?fit=370%2C130" /></a>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<h2>Learning Emacs</h2>\n<h3>起</h3>\n<p>还在Kotei的时候, 跟着一个Tuts+教程, 花了4天熟悉Vim.<br />\n从此入了Vim阵营, 感叹它在啥环境下都有.<br />\n那时也留下了学习emacs的念想.<br />\n这么多年过去, 是时候付诸实践啦~</p>\n<p>会持续在此更新相关笔记.</p>\n<h3>注解</h3>\n<p><code>C</code>代表<code>Ctrl</code>键</p>\n<p><code>M</code>代表<code>Meta</code>键(<code>Alt</code>键)</p>\n<h3>Operations</h3>\n<p>终止emacs会话<code>C-x C-c</code></p>\n<p>退出正在键入的命令<code>C-g</code></p>\n<h3>Screen-moving Operations</h3>\n<p>下一屏<code>C-v</code>, 上一屏<code>M-v</code></p>\n<p>光标所在字符的 居中/居上/居下<code>C-l</code></p>\n<h3>Cursor-moving Operations</h3>\n<p>前一行<code>C-p</code> (Previous line)<br />\n退一格<code>C-b</code> (Backward)<br />\n进一格<code>C-f</code> (Forward)<br />\n下一行<code>C-n</code> (Next line)</p>\n<p>进一词<code>M-f</code> (Forward)<br />\n退一词<code>M-b</code> (Backward)</p>\n<p>行头<code>C-a</code><br />\n行尾<code>C-e</code><br />\n句头<code>M-a</code><br />\n句尾<code>M-e</code></p>\n<p>篇头<code>M-&lt;</code><br />\n篇尾<code>M-&gt;</code><br />\n<code>&lt;&gt;</code>键都处于上键位置, 所以输入时是需要按住<code>Shift</code>键.</p>\n<p>位移命令可接受数字参数, 使用<code>C-u</code>录入数字, 然后会被重复作用到后续的位移命令上.<br />\n按住<code>M</code>输入数字也等同于此操作.<br />\n例如<code>C-u 8 C-f</code>会前进8个字符.</p>\n<h3>Author</h3>\n<p>Luo Yu<br />\nFriday, September 8, 2017</p>\n\n\t\t\t</div><!-- .entry-content -->\n\n    <footer class="entry-footer">\n        <span class="cat-links">Posted in <a href="http://198.11.180.45/category/dev/" rel="category tag">dev</a></span><span class="tags-links">Tagged <a href="http://198.11.180.45/tag/basic/" rel="tag">basic</a>, <a href="http://198.11.180.45/tag/emacs/" rel="tag">emacs</a></span>    </footer><!-- .entry-footer -->\n</article><!-- #post-## -->\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n<article id="post-667" class="post-667 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-dev tag-bluemix tag-cloudfoundry tag-hubot tag-nodejs">\n \t<header class="entry-header">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2017/09/bluemix-hubot/" rel="bookmark">Bluemix 试用</a></h2>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class="entry-meta">\n\t\t\t<span class="posted-on"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2017/09/bluemix-hubot/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2017-09-02T12:24:21+08:00">2017-09-02</time><time class="updated" datetime="2017-09-02T14:43:02+08:00">2017-09-02</time></a></span><span class="byline"> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://198.11.180.45/author/yul/">Rick Luo</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2017/09/bluemix-hubot/#respond">Leave a comment</a></span>\t\t</div><!-- .entry-meta -->\n\t\t\t</header><!-- .entry-header -->\n\n\t<div class="entry-content">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="post-thumbnail">\n\t\t\t\t<a href="http://198.11.180.45/2017/09/bluemix-hubot/"><img width="370" height="130" src="https://i2.wp.com/198.11.180.45/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/bluemix-hubot-spe.jpg?fit=370%2C130" class="attachment-libre-2-post-thumbnail size-libre-2-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" data-attachment-id="675" data-permalink="http://198.11.180.45/bluemix-hubot-spe/" data-orig-file="https://i2.wp.com/198.11.180.45/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/bluemix-hubot-spe.jpg?fit=370%2C130" data-orig-size="370,130" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="bluemix-hubot-spe" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://i2.wp.com/198.11.180.45/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/bluemix-hubot-spe.jpg?fit=300%2C105" data-large-file="https://i2.wp.com/198.11.180.45/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/bluemix-hubot-spe.jpg?fit=370%2C130" /></a>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<h3>Bluemix 试用</h3>\n<h4>账号</h4>\n<p>官网注册一下bluemix的账号, 如果之前注册过IBM的账号的话, 可以直接拿来登录并激活该功能.</p>\n<p>(有部分Script似乎在墙外, 最好翻一下操作).</p>\n<h4>创建空间</h4>\n<p>首次登入, 会被告知试用天数, 和简单的收费介绍, 大概就是超出免费使用额的时候进行收费.</p>\n<p>然后呢, 会有一个指引, 来创建&#8221;组织名称&#8221;>&#8221;空间名称&#8221;. 这里也会选择服务器物理位置. 自动给我匹配了一个“悉尼”, 看似最近的也只有这个了.</p>\n<h4>创建服务</h4>\n<p>选一个服务吧. 各类应用容器&#8230;(这样算, 一个服务一份钱?).</p>\n<p>因为要部署的是<a href="https://github.com/hubotio/hubot">Hubot</a>, 一个NodeJS做的程序, 所以这里就直接选个CloudFoundry的Node.js应用类型就行啦.</p>\n<p>同样, 创建好名称, 比如我这里就叫“nodejshubot”.</p>\n<p>创建完后, 系统会自动为你启动该服务.</p>\n<h4>准备工具</h4>\n<p>bluemix环境已有, 接下来就是获取hubot并部署到该服务中.</p>\n<p>那这个环境是一个CloudFoundry环境, 就需要它的交互工具.</p>\n<p>在macOS中, 还是老一套, 用Homebrew来安装吧:</p>\n<pre><code class="bash">brew install cloudfoundry/tap/cf-cli\n</code></pre>\n<p>使用<code>cf</code>命令测试了一下,</p>\n<pre><code class="bash">$ cf\ncf version 6.30.0+decf883fc.2017-09-01, Cloud Foundry command line tool\nUsage: cf [global options] command [arguments...] [command options]\n</code></pre>\n<p>挺正常的.</p>\n<p>然后还需要git和node环境, 如果你还没有的话.</p>\n<p>下载安装过Xcode的, 都会由Command Line Tools附带安装了git.</p>\n<p>node环境, 也是可以直接<code>brew install</code>的.</p>\n<h4>获取Hubot</h4>\n<pre><code class="bash">$ git clone git@github.com:hubotio/hubot.git\nCloning into \'hubot\'...\nremote: Counting objects: 8746, done.\nremote: Total 8746 (delta 0), reused 0 (delta 0), pack-reused 8746\nReceiving objects: 100% (8746/8746), 1.91 MiB | 117.00 KiB/s, done.\nResolving deltas: 100% (4926/4926), done.\n</code></pre>\n<p>官方解释到:</p>\n<p>如果要部署到 Bluemix，设置 manifest.yml 文件会很有用。manifest.yml 包含有关应用程序的基本信息，例如名称、要为每个实例分配的内存量以及路径。</p>\n<p>那我们就在这个项目里创建一个manifest.yml文件, name呢就是我们的应用程序名称.</p>\n<pre><code class="yml">---\napplications:\n- name: nodejshubot\n  command: ./bin/hubot --adapter slack\n  instances: 1\n  memory: 256M\n</code></pre>\n<h4>部署应用程序</h4>\n<p>到了用Cloud Foundry CLI的地方啦.</p>\n<pre><code class="bash">cf api &lt;API-endpoint&gt;\n</code></pre>\n<p>API-endpoint呢 则是前面选好的区域, 比如我选的悉尼.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align="left">API 端点</th>\n<th align="left">区域</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align="left">https://api.ng.bluemix.net</td>\n<td align="left">美国南部</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align="left">https://api.eu-gb.bluemix.net</td>\n<td align="left">英国</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align="left">https://api.au-syd.bluemix.net</td>\n<td align="left">悉尼</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>实际使用:</p>\n<pre><code class="bash">$ cf api https://api.au-syd.bluemix.net\nSetting api endpoint to https://api.au-syd.bluemix.net...\nOK\n\napi endpoint:   https://api.au-syd.bluemix.net\napi version:    2.75.0\nNot logged in. Use \'cf login\' to log in.\n</code></pre>\n<p>那么就是OK的了, 都提示好让我直接login:</p>\n<pre><code class="bash">$ cf login\nAPI endpoint: https://api.au-syd.bluemix.net\n\nEmail&gt; blodely@gmail.com\nPassword&gt;\n\nAuthenticating...\nOK\n\nTargeted org blodelyAtSyd\n\nTargeted space dev\n\nAPI endpoint:   https://api.au-syd.bluemix.net (API version: 2.75.0)\nUser:           blodely@gmail.com\nOrg:            blodelyAtSyd\nSpace:          dev\n</code></pre>\n<p>这就可以从程序目录push应用程序到bluemix了(感觉这个架构很重):</p>\n<pre><code class="bash">$ cf push\nUsing manifest file /Users/blodely/Desktop/bluemixhubot/hubot/manifest.yml\n\nUpdating app nodejshubot in org blodelyAtSyd / space dev as blodely@gmail.com...\nOK\n\nUploading nodejshubot...\nUploading app files from: /Users/blodely/Desktop/bluemixhubot/hubot\nUploading 85K, 64 files\nDone uploading\nOK\n\nStopping app nodejshubot in org blodelyAtSyd / space dev as blodely@gmail.com...\nOK\n\nStarting app nodejshubot in org blodelyAtSyd / space dev as blodely@gmail.com...\nDownloading liberty-for-java_v3_11-20170710-0312...\n# 省略省略大段的远端环境自动下载配置的信息...\nStaging complete\nUploading droplet, build artifacts cache...\nUploading build artifacts cache...\nUploading droplet...\nUploaded build artifacts cache (1.2M)\nUploaded droplet (18.8M)\nUploading complete\nDestroying container\nSuccessfully destroyed container\n\n0 of 1 instances running, 1 starting\n1 of 1 instances running\n\nApp started\n\n\nOK\n\nApp nodejshubot was started using this command `npm start`\n\nShowing health and status for app nodejshubot in org blodelyAtSyd / space dev as blodely@gmail.com...\nOK\n\nrequested state: started\ninstances: 1/1\nusage: 256M x 1 instances\nurls: nodejshubot.au-syd.mybluemix.net\nlast uploaded: Sat Sep 2 04:10:43 UTC 2017\nstack: cflinuxfs2\nbuildpack: SDK for Node.js(TM) (ibm-node.js-6.11.1, buildpack-v3.13-20170725-1347)\n\n     state     since                    cpu    memory          disk          details\n#0   running   2017-09-02 12:12:13 PM   0.2%   48.7M of 256M   75.4M of 1G\n</code></pre>\n<p>这就push成功，应用也启动了.</p>\n<p>状态也列举出来在最后面, manifest中写到的一样, 指派了256M内存的使用(???).</p>\n<h3>Author</h3>\n<p>骆昱, September 2, 2017</p>\n<p>indie.luo@gmail.com</p>\n\n\t\t\t</div><!-- .entry-content -->\n\n    <footer class="entry-footer">\n        <span class="cat-links">Posted in <a href="http://198.11.180.45/category/dev/" rel="category tag">dev</a></span><span class="tags-links">Tagged <a href="http://198.11.180.45/tag/bluemix/" rel="tag">bluemix</a>, <a href="http://198.11.180.45/tag/cloudfoundry/" rel="tag">cloudfoundry</a>, <a href="http://198.11.180.45/tag/hubot/" rel="tag">hubot</a>, <a href="http://198.11.180.45/tag/nodejs/" rel="tag">nodejs</a></span>    </footer><!-- .entry-footer -->\n</article><!-- #post-## -->\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n<article id="post-663" class="post-663 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-dev tag-kitura tag-server tag-swift">\n \t<header class="entry-header">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2017/09/kitura-framework/" rel="bookmark">Kitura framework</a></h2>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class="entry-meta">\n\t\t\t<span class="posted-on"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2017/09/kitura-framework/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2017-09-02T09:51:46+08:00">2017-09-02</time><time class="updated" datetime="2017-09-02T09:58:07+08:00">2017-09-02</time></a></span><span class="byline"> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://198.11.180.45/author/yul/">Rick Luo</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://198.11.180.45/2017/09/kitura-framework/#respond">Leave a comment</a></span>\t\t</div><!-- .entry-meta -->\n\t\t\t</header><!-- .entry-header -->\n\n\t<div class="entry-content">\n\t\t<h3>Index</h3>\n<h5>Kitura</h5>\n<h5>使用Kitura框架</h5>\n<h5>部署到服务器</h5>\n<h5>Author</h5>\n<h3>Kitura</h3>\n<p>不用多介绍了，Kitura差不多是一岁了. 来自IBM的Swift框架(on server-side).</p>\n<p>自Swift开源以来，大家都在进行各个平台的尝试.</p>\n<p>相关较成熟的解决方案有<a href="http://perfect.org/">Perfect框架</a>, Kitura则相对来说较为轻量级.</p>\n<p><a href="http://www.kitura.io/">Official site</a>, <a href="https://github.com/IBM-Swift">Github</a>.</p>\n<p>现在的优势是该Swift框架在IBM的Bluemix上已有应用服务了，当然Swift容器也有的.</p>\n<h3>使用Kitura框架</h3>\n<p>照例使用Swift Package Manager创建:</p>\n<pre><code class="bash">swift package init --type executable\n</code></pre>\n<p>修改Package.swift，添加Kitura框架的依赖:</p>\n<pre><code class="swift">import PackageDescription\n\nlet package = Package(\n    name: "myFirstProject",\n    dependencies: [\n        .Package(url: "https://github.com/IBM-Swift/Kitura.git", majorVersion: 1, minor: 7)\n    ])\n</code></pre>\n<p>Build一下:</p>\n<pre><code>swift build\n</code></pre>\n<p>首次Build就会看到一个个依赖包被克隆下来啦.</p>\n<p>修改Main.swift文件，添加服务入口:</p>\n<pre><code class="swift">import Kitura\n\n// Create a new router\nlet router = Router()\n\n// Handle HTTP GET requests to /\nrouter.get("/") {\n    request, response, next in\n    response.send("Hello, World!")\n    next()\n}\n\n// Add an HTTP server and connect it to the router\nKitura.addHTTPServer(onPort: 8080, with: router)\n\n// Start the Kitura runloop (this call never returns)\nKitura.run()\n</code></pre>\n<p>然后就可以跑起程序试试了:</p>\n<pre><code class="bash">swift build\n.build/debug/myFirstProject\n</code></pre>\n<h3>部署到服务器 deploy</h3>\n<p>这里有个比较坑的地方, 追根溯源, 还是来自Apple的. 目前Swift给出的包都是为了Ubuntu环境准备的, 有14.04LTS, 有16.04LTS的. 其他环境得自己编译.</p>\n<p>这里呢, 我偷懒点, 使用最爱的docker来部署.</p>\n<p><code>ibmcom/swift-ubuntu</code>是一个Swift Ready的Ubuntu14环境，可以直接拿来用.</p>\n<h3>作者 Author</h3>\n<p>骆昱/Luo Yu, indie.luo@gmai.com</p>\n<p>Saturday, September 2, 2017</p>\n\n\t\t\t</div><!-- .entry-content -->\n\n    <footer class="entry-footer">\n        <span class="cat-links">Posted in <a href="http://198.11.180.45/category/dev/" rel="category tag">dev</a></span><span class="tags-links">Tagged <a href="http://198.11.180.45/tag/kitura/" rel="tag">kitura</a>, <a href="http://198.11.180.45/tag/server/" rel="tag">server</a>, <a href="http://198.11.180.45/tag/swift/" rel="tag">swift</a></span>    </footer><!-- .entry-footer -->\n</article><!-- #post-## -->\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t<nav class="navigation posts-navigation" id="icon-amazon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">\n<path d="M13.582,8.182C11.934,8.367,9.78,8.49,8.238,9.166c-1.781,0.769-3.03,2.337-3.03,4.644 c0,2.953,1.86,4.429,4.253,4.429c2.02,0,3.125-0.477,4.685-2.065c0.516,0.747,0.685,1.109,1.629,1.894 c0.212,0.114,0.483,0.103,0.672-0.066l0.006,0.006c0.567-0.505,1.599-1.401,2.18-1.888c0.231-0.188,0.19-0.496,0.009-0.754 c-0.52-0.718-1.072-1.303-1.072-2.634V8.305c0-1.876,0.133-3.599-1.249-4.891C15.23,2.369,13.422,2,12.04,2 If the header value is not present in the charset conversion table, a fallback mechanism is used to truncate it to a two characters value to allow a quick retry (for example, 'en-US' is truncated to 'en'). A header value of less than two characters forces an out of bound write of one NUL byte to a memory location that is not part of the string. In the worst case, quite unlikely, the process would crash which could be used as a Denial of Service attack. If the header value is not present in the charset conversion table, a fallback mechanism is used to truncate it to a two characters value to allow a quick retry (for example, 'en-US' is truncated to 'en'). A header value of less than two characters forces an out of bound write of one NUL byte to a memory location that is not part of the string. In the worst case, quite unlikely, the process would crash which could be used as a Denial of Service attack. With 5.x after 5.6.28 or 7.x after 7.0.13, the issue is resolved in a non-default configuration with the opcache.validate_permission=1 setting. The vulnerability details are as follows. In PHP SAPIs where PHP interpreters share a common parent process, Zend OpCache creates a shared memory object owned by the common parent during initialization. Child PHP processes inherit the SHM descriptor, using it to cache and retrieve compiled script bytecode ("opcode" in PHP jargon). Cache keys vary depending on configuration, but filename is a central key component, and compiled opcode can generally be run if a script\'s filename is known or can be guessed. Many common shared-hosting configurations change EUID in child processes to enforce privilege separation among hosted users (for example using mod_ruid2 for the Apache HTTP Server, or php-fpm user settings). In these scenarios, the default Zend OpCache behavior defeats script file permissions by sharing a single SHM cache among all child PHP processes. PHP scripts often contain sensitive information: Think of CMS configurations where reading or running another user\'s script usually means gaining privileges to the CMS database.'}, 'CVE-2018-14883': {'references': ['http://php.net/ChangeLog-5.php', 'http://php.net/ChangeLog-7.php', 'http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/104871', 'https://bugs.php.net/bug.php?id=76423', 'https://lists.debian.org/debian-lts-announce/2018/09/msg00000.html', 'https://security.netapp.com/advisory/ntap-20181107-0003/', 'https://usn.ubuntu.com/3766-1/', 'https://usn.ubuntu.com/3766-2/', 'https://www.debian.org/security/2018/dsa-4353', 'https://www.tenable.com/security/tns-2018-12'], 'verified': False, 'cvss': '5.0', 'summary': 'An issue was discovered in PHP before 5.6.37, 7.0.x before 7.0.31, 7.1.x before 7.1.20, and 7.2.x before 7.2.8. With 5.x after 5.6.28 or 7.x after 7.0.13, the issue is resolved in a non-default configuration with the opcache.validate_permission=1 setting. The vulnerability details are as follows. In PHP SAPIs where PHP interpreters share a common parent process, Zend OpCache creates a shared memory object owned by the common parent during initialization. Child PHP processes inherit the SHM descriptor, using it to cache and retrieve compiled script bytecode ("opcode" in PHP jargon). Cache keys vary depending on configuration, but filename is a central key component, and compiled opcode can generally be run if a script\'s filename is known or can be guessed. Many common shared-hosting configurations change EUID in child processes to enforce privilege separation among hosted users (for example using mod_ruid2 for the Apache HTTP Server, or php-fpm user settings). In these scenarios, the default Zend OpCache behavior defeats script file permissions by sharing a single SHM cache among all child PHP processes.   <div class="main_page">\n      <div class="page_header floating_element">\n        <img src="/icons/openlogo-75.png" alt="Debian Logo" class="floating_element"/>\n        <span class="floating_element">\n          Apache2 Debian Default Page\n        </span>\n      </div>\n<!--      <div class="table_of_contents floating_element">\n        <div class="section_header section_header_grey">\n          TABLE OF CONTENTS\n        </div>\n        <div class="table_of_contents_item floating_element">\n          <a href="#about">About</a>\n        </div>\n        <div class="table_of_contents_item floating_element">\n          <a href="#changes">Changes</a>\n        </div>\n        <div class="table_of_contents_item floating_element">\n          <a href="#scope">Scope</a>\n        </div>\n        <div class="table_of_contents_item floating_element">\n          <a href="#files">Config files</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n-->\n      <div class="content_section floating_element">\n\n\n        <div class="section_header section_header_red">\n          <div id="about"></div>\n          It works!\n        </div>\n        <div class="content_section_text">\n          <p>\n                This is the default welcome page used to test the correct \n                operation of the Apache2 server after installation on Debian systems.\n                If you can read this page, it means that the Apache HTTP server installed at\n                this site is working properly. You should <b>replace this file</b> (located at\n                <tt>/var/www/html/index.html</tt>) before continuing to operate your HTTP server.\n          </p>\n\n\n          <p>\n                If you are a normal user of this web site and don\'t know what this page is\n                about, this probably means that the site is currently unavailable due to\n                maintenance.\n                If the problem persists, please contact the site\'s administrator.\n          </p>\n\n        </div>\n        <div class="section_header">\n          <div id="changes"></div>\n                Configuration Overview\n        </div>\n        <div class="content_section_text">\n          <p>\n                Debian\'s Apache2 default configuration is different from the\n                upstream default configuration, and split into several files optimized for\n                interaction with Debian tools. The configuration system is\n                <b>fully documented in\n                /usr/share/doc/apache2/README.Debian.gz</b>. Refer to this for the full\n                documentation. Documentation for the web server itself can be\n                found by accessing the <a href="/manual">manual</a> if the <tt>apache2-doc</tt>\n                package was installed on this server.\n\n          </p>\n          <p>\n                The configuration layout for an Apache2 web server installation on Debian systems is as follows:\n          </p>\n          <pre>\n/etc/apache2/\n|-- apache2.conf\n|       `--  ports.conf\n|-- mods-enabled\n|       |-- *.load\n|       `-- *.conf\n|-- conf-enabled\n|       `-- *.conf\n|-- sites-enabled\n|       `-- *.conf\n          </pre>\n          <ul>\n                        <li>\n                           <tt>apache2.conf</tt> is the main configuration\n                           file. It puts the pieces together by including all remaining configuration\n                           files when starting up the web server.\n                        </li>\n\n                        <li>\n                           <tt>ports.conf</tt> is always included from the\n                           main configuration file. It is used to determine the listening ports for\n                           incoming connections, and this file can be customized anytime.\n                        </li>\n\n                        <li>\n                           Configuration files in the <tt>mods-enabled/</tt>,\n                           <tt>conf-enabled/</tt> and <tt>sites-enabled/</tt> directories contain\n                           particular configuration snippets which manage modules, global configuration\n                           fragments, or virtual host configurations, respectively.\n                        </li>\n\n                        <li>\n                           They are activated by symlinking available\n                           configuration files from their respective\n                           *-available/ counterparts. These should be managed\n                           by using our helpers\n                           <tt>\n                                a2enmod,\n                                a2dismod,\n                           </tt>\n                           <tt>\n                                a2ensite,\n                                a2dissite,\n                            </tt>\n                                and\n                           <tt>\n                                a2enconf,\n                                a2disconf\n                           </tt>. See their respective man pages for detailed information.\n                        </li>\n\n                        <li>\n                           The binary is called apache2. Due to the use of\n                           environment variables, in the default configuration, apache2 needs to be\n                           started/stopped with <tt>/etc/init.d/apache2</tt> or <tt>apache2ctl</tt>.\n                           <b>Calling <tt>/usr/bin/apache2</tt> directly will not work</b> with the\n                           default configuration.\n                        </li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class="section_header">\n            <div id="docroot"></div>\n                Document Roots\n        </div>\n\n        <div class="content_section_text">\n            <p>\n                By default, Debian does not allow access through the web browser to\n                <em>any</em> file apart of those located in <tt>/var/www</tt>,\n                <a href="http://httpd.apache.org/docs/2.4/mod/mod_userdir.html" rel="nofollow">public_html</a>\n                directories (when enabled) and <tt>/usr/share</tt> (for web\n                applications). If your site is using a web document root\n                located elsewhere (such as in <tt>/srv</tt>) you may need to whitelist your\n                document root directory in <tt>/etc/apache2/apache2.conf</tt>.\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                The default Debian document root is <tt>/var/www/html</tt>. You\n                can make your own virtual hosts under /var/www. This is different\n                to previous releases which provides better security out of the box.\n            </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class="section_header">\n          <div id="bugs"></div>\n                Reporting Problems\n        </div>\n        <div class="content_section_text">\n          <p>\n                Please use the <tt>reportbug</tt> tool to report bugs in the\n                Apache2 package with Debian. However, check <a\n                href="http://bugs.debian.org/cgi-bin/pkgreport.cgi?ordering=normal;archive=0;src=apache2;repeatmerged=0"\n                rel="nofollow">existing bug reports</a> before reporting a new bug.\n          </p>\n          <p>\n                Please report bugs specific to modules (such as PHP and others)\n                to respective packages, not to the web server itself.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n\n\n\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class="validator">\n    </div>\n  </body>\n</html>\n\n', 'location': '/', 'components': {}, 'server': 'Apache/2.4.10 (Debian)', 'sitemap': None, 'securitytxt_hash': None}, 'port': 92, 'hostnames': [], 'location': {'city': 'Paris', 'region_code': 'A8', 'area_code': None, 'longitude': 2.329199999999986, 'country_code3': 'FRA', 'country_name': 'France', 'postal_code': '75001', 'dma_code': None, 'country_code': 'FR', 'latitude': 48.86279999999999}, 'timestamp': '2019-07-08T03:42:18.111950', 'domains': [], 'org': 'ONLINE SAS', 'data': 'HTTP/1.1 200 OK\r\nDate: Mon, 20 Nov 2017 20:37:14 GMT\r\nServer: Apache/2.4.10 (Debian)\r\nLast-Modified: Mon, 14 Aug 2017 10:37:10 GMT\r\nETag: "29cd-556b43ec205e9"\r\nAccept-Ranges: bytes\r\nContent-Length: 10701\r\nVary: Accept-Encoding\r\nContent-Type: text/html\r\n\r\n', 'asn': 'AS12876', 'transport': 'tcp', 'ip_str': '62.210.48.195'}

                 <div class="curved container">\r\n                        <h3>Managing Tomcat</h3>\r\n                        <p>For security, access to the <a href="/manager/html">manager webapp</a> is restricted.\r\n                        Users are defined in:</p>\r\n                        <pre>$CATALINA_HOME/conf/tomcat-users.xml</pre>\r\n                        <p>In Tomcat 7.0 access to the manager application is split between\r\n                           different users. &nbsp; <a href="/docs/manager-howto.html">Read more...</a></p>\r\n                        <br />\r\n
